data.description: GREAT LOCATION IN MILLERSPORT...Directly across from the Elementary School and a few steps from shopping, coffee shops, restaurants, and Buckeye Lake.Loads of opportunity with this 3 BDR 2 Full Bath home with open concept Living/Kitchen Area.  Owner suite full bath includes a step in shower w/ hand held option shower head, grab bars and room to move. (Tiled)  Laundry room includes shower and H2O tank. Nearly a half acre lot you will LOVE the spacious rear yard, lard rear enclosed deck w/ small fenced area for your furry family member.  Shed stays.
